The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Split verdict on smoking
                                                                                                            Split verdict on smoking
                            
	New Delhi, Feb. 7 (PTI): Delhi High Court today gave a split verdict on a petition challenging a government notification for banning smoking scenes in films and in television programmes.        
	A division bench of Justices Mukul Mudgal and Sanjiv Khanna, deciding the petition of film producer and director Mahesh Bhatt, referred the case to the chief justice.                                                                                                                                                                            
